{"tid":82163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]美圖秀秀推出「跨次元相機」，自拍變成華麗風小說插圖","createTime":"2017-01-15T18:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T15:16:37.000Z","uid":74952,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbc6f95a91ba461efd4adbe044f3007b134a998","tid":82163,"uid":74952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"好柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/meitu_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmeitu_4.jpg&h=be2821fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/meitu_1xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmeitu_1xx.jpg&h=e89b5a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/meitua_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmeitua_2.jpg&h=76e6cefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/meitu_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmeitu_3.jpg&h=b4ed28e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美圖秀秀更新後，加入了「跨次元相機」功能，可以把自拍照變成手繪風照片，特效分別為天使之戀、十里桃花、童話萌主、櫻之少女、人魚眼淚、暗夜女爵&hellip;&hellip;。雖然這濾鏡是為女性用家準備，不過由於效果實在太誇張，不少男生都踴躍測試，目前可見 facebook 也出現了大量的測試圖。<br />\n<br />\n根據報導，美圖秀秀表示，之所以上線這個功能，是因為從市場上看到了用戶的需求。 「現在網上出售手繪畫像的店舖有很多，價位從十幾到幾十元不等，月銷量可達數千單，但往往可能需要等很多天才能得到一張定制的手繪畫像。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/180474/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%96%E7%A7%80%E7%A7%80%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E3%80%8C%E8%B7%A8%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%83%E7%9B%B8%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C